## Quality Checklist

### Storytelling Review Checklist
- [ ] Story follows the transformation arc (setup, conflict, transformation, resolution)
- [ ] Character is relatable to target audience (ambitious men 18-35)
- [ ] Story demonstrates FastLane/SideLane/SlowLane framework
- [ ] Results are specific and verifiable
- [ ] Challenges and failures are included
- [ ] Story aligns with Trajectory brand values
- [ ] Emotional resonance is strong and authentic
- [ ] Call-to-action is clear and compelling
- [ ] Story supports the overall brand narrative
- [ ] Content is original and not generic
